Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 04 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Cardiovascular/Thoracic aorta' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Aortic anomalies' radio button is enabled
And 'Aortic aneurysm' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Aortic anomalies' radio button
Then radio buttons in "Anomalies" column are enabled

When I select 'Aortic coarctation/ Coarctatio aortae' radio button
Then checkboxes in "Details aortic coarctation/ coarctatio aortae" column are enabled